                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-259-off1368 t18300114-259-cd1369"></join>, 4 lbs. weight of candles, value 2s. 4d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t18300114-259-victim1734" type="victimName">
                  Joseph 
                  Little
               <interp inst="t18300114-259-victim1734" type="surname" value="Little"></interp>
